WEBVTT

00:00:57.977 --> 00:01:02.139
FRIDA DAVIDOVITSH, KARETET MISPAR ARBA

00:01:04.727 --> 00:01:07.994
VEAT NOSAAT IM CHAVEROT SHELACH

00:01:08.018 --> 00:01:08.906
yo

00:01:08.473 --> 00:01:10.930
BERAKEVET LEKIVUN HABAYIT

00:01:10.110 --> 00:01:11.099
yo.

00:01:11.545 --> 00:01:14.138
forn mir shoyn mitn RAKEVET

00:01:14.565 --> 00:01:15.954
kumen mir on

00:01:15.954 --> 00:01:16.955
far

00:01:18.025 --> 00:01:19.538
BRATISLAVA

00:01:21.282 --> 00:01:24.364
kumen aroyf yidishe mener

00:01:26.023 --> 00:01:28.143
un zey zogn

00:01:28.487 --> 00:01:30.911
mir zoln mir aropkumen funem tsug

00:01:31.558 --> 00:01:35.031
zenen geshtanen oytos, hobn mentshn gevart dortn

00:01:35.031 --> 00:01:36.902
zoln mir geyn mit di oytos

00:01:36.942 --> 00:01:40.564
far di rusishe geyen aroyf in tsug

00:01:40.587 --> 00:01:43.466
un dos iz shreklekh vos zey tuen mit di froyen.

00:01:44.670 --> 00:01:46.520
undz ze'mir aropgegangen.

00:01:46.543 --> 00:01:48.827
zey hobn undz mit di oytos

00:01:48.827 --> 00:01:52.123
arayngefirt. dort iz shoyn geven organizirt

00:01:52.281 --> 00:01:57.827
shtiber far azane mentshn vi undz ze'mir, shoyn gevezn merer froyen dortn

00:01:58.069 --> 00:02:01.221
un m'iz oykhet nor oyf der erd geshlofn

00:02:01.221 --> 00:02:04.948
ober BECHOL ZOT zenen mir gevezn bavornt

00:02:06.625 --> 00:02:09.555
zenen mir dort oykhet a por tog opgezesn

00:02:10.741 --> 00:02:15.680
mit zeyer veynik esn, far s'iz nokh nisht geven. s'iz geven nokh der n- milkhome.

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:19.359
nu, ikh hob mimeyle nisht gedarft a sakh.

00:02:20.833 --> 00:02:25.872
dortn bin ikh gelign, bin ikh zeyer, zeyer krank gevezn

00:02:29.828 --> 00:02:32.792
fun a zakh vos ikh hob shoyn befor dertseylt

00:02:33.287 --> 00:02:38.596
vos iz forgekumen mit di froyen un vos m'hot nisht gekent, vos iz geven nisht ayngenumen

00:02:40.105 --> 00:02:44.723
un s'iz mir nisht ayngenumen tsu dertseyln dos, ober ikh hob zeyer gelitn derfun.

00:02:48.070 --> 00:02:49.262
dernokh

00:02:49.268 --> 00:02:52.181
zenen mir ge- dortn gevezn a por teg

00:02:53.115 --> 00:02:55.404
biz vi lang s'iz gekumen shoyn

00:02:55.815 --> 00:03:00.821
a bafel di yidn, m'hot zikh shoyn mer tsunoyfgenumen un mer mitgeholfn

00:03:01.553 --> 00:03:04.044
biz m'hot undz vider oyfgezetst

00:03:04.928 --> 00:03:07.605
oyfn tsug un zenen mir geforn

00:03:07.763 --> 00:03:08.955
vayter.

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:13.781
ZEHU. m'iz geforn.

00:03:14.732 --> 00:03:17.561
m'iz geforn. m'iz ongekumen aheym

00:03:19.727 --> 00:03:22.809
un m'hot nisht getrofn keynem in der heym.

00:03:25.701 --> 00:03:29.604
es iz gevezn zeyer shver, zeyer shver

00:03:29.604 --> 00:03:31.921
tsu farlirn aza mishpokhe

00:03:34.122 --> 00:03:35.384
eltern

00:03:35.384 --> 00:03:36.866
mit kinder

00:03:38.931 --> 00:03:42.739
mit geshvister mit feters mit mumes.

00:03:45.799 --> 00:03:47.649
s'iz geven a shvere zakh.

00:03:47.925 --> 00:03:49.792
zeyer a shvere zakh.

00:03:52.161 --> 00:03:54.258
s'iz geven shver dos lebn

00:03:54.258 --> 00:03:56.103
zenen mir ongekumen aheym

00:03:58.033 --> 00:03:58.989
um

00:03:59.350 --> 00:04:01.268
um, in yuli

00:04:01.425 --> 00:04:02.279
in yuli.

00:04:03.585 --> 00:04:09.758
in yuli iz nisht geven shoyn keyn alte zakhn vos tsu esn, nisht keyn kartofl, nisht keyn gornisht

00:04:09.758 --> 00:04:13.653
un keyn naye zakhn iz nokh nisht gevezn, nisht do, nisht dort.

00:04:14.065 --> 00:04:17.293
s'iz geven shver, shreklekh shver, dos esn

00:04:17.293 --> 00:04:18.343
dos lebn.

00:04:20.123 --> 00:04:24.369
nor ikh, azoy dortn hobn mir gehat goyishe shkheynim

00:04:24.477 --> 00:04:28.335
un s'iz gevezn eyn shkheyne an eltere froy

00:04:28.982 --> 00:04:35.138
vos mir ze'mir geven zeyer gut mit ir shtendik, un zi iz BEEMET nisht gevezn keyn antisemitke.

00:04:35.138 --> 00:04:36.991
zi iz geven a frume

00:04:37.183 --> 00:04:39.944
un zi iz gevezn zeyer a gute

00:04:40.086 --> 00:04:43.084
un tsu mir iz zi zeyer gut gevezn.

00:04:43.140 --> 00:04:44.737
zi fleg alts mir

00:04:44.997 --> 00:04:46.875
"kum arayn, kum arayn"

00:04:46.875 --> 00:04:49.175
mir alts gegebn epes esn.

00:04:50.177 --> 00:04:51.892
biz ikh hob mikh aleyn

00:04:52.759 --> 00:04:53.850
genumen

00:04:54.328 --> 00:04:56.752
az ikh zol aleyn hobn vos

00:04:57.265 --> 00:04:59.267
vos se kumt, vos tsu esn.

00:05:00.403 --> 00:05:03.991
AT SIPART LI KODEM SHEAT UNK HABAITA

00:05:03.542 --> 00:05:04.430
yo

00:05:04.133 --> 00:05:06.658
VEYESH UNK SHAM ANASHIM BITOCH HABAIT.

00:05:06.073 --> 00:05:07.032
yo

00:05:07.032 --> 00:05:10.927
ober ikh hob di mentshn aro- ober ikh bin geblibn in a lere shtub

00:05:10.967 --> 00:05:11.940
far m'hot a-

00:05:11.940 --> 00:05:14.521
ales fun undzer shtub aroysgetrogn.

00:05:14.798 --> 00:05:20.119
undz ho'mir gehat, undz ho'mir gevoynt zeyer sheyn. undz ze'mir gevezn balebatishe mentshn.

00:05:20.119 --> 00:05:22.549
undz ho'mir gehat zeyer sheyn mebl

00:05:22.549 --> 00:05:25.490
zeyer sheyn ales ayngeordnt.

00:05:25.513 --> 00:05:28.544
m'iz gekumen bavundern undzer WOHNUNG.

00:05:28.888 --> 00:05:32.898
mayn mame, zol zikh mien, iz gevezn zeyer a groyse baleboste.

00:05:33.141 --> 00:05:35.075
az s'iz gekumen a mol

00:05:35.301 --> 00:05:38.681
zi hot zikh gemakht tseyn bayn a tseyn dokter

00:05:38.681 --> 00:05:41.252
un zi hot gedarft geyn di tseyn mestn

00:05:41.258 --> 00:05:45.001
un s'iz nisht geven fartik di tseyn, hot men geshikt dos

00:05:45.001 --> 00:05:49.599
meydl vos hot bay zey gearbet, zol kumen zogn der mame zol nisht kumen

00:05:49.599 --> 00:05:51.495
di tseyn zenen nisht fertik.

00:05:52.108 --> 00:05:55.696
zi hot dos ale mol gedenkt

00:05:56.158 --> 00:06:00.534
afile nokh do in land, zi hot gev- zi lebt shoyn nisht. zi hot gevoynt in RECHOVOT.

00:06:00.534 --> 00:06:03.411
ven zi iz gekumen tsu mir, hot zi vider a mol gezogt

00:06:03.411 --> 00:06:05.689
ven zi iz gekumen zogn der mame

00:06:05.689 --> 00:06:07.579
az zi zol nisht gekumen di tseyn a-

00:06:07.579 --> 00:06:09.821
mestn, hot zi moyre gehat

00:06:10.350 --> 00:06:13.114
ah ts- arayntsugeyn in shtub.

00:06:13.114 --> 00:06:16.841
zi hot geefnt di tir, un zi hot nisht gevust vi azoy ar-

00:06:17.083 --> 00:06:21.046
zi hot, zi hot moyre gehat arayntsutretn in shtub, vi azoy bayn undz iz gevezn

00:06:21.046 --> 00:06:21.839
shtark

00:06:21.839 --> 00:06:22.767
reyn

00:06:22.767 --> 00:06:25.262
un shtark ayngeordnt di shtub.

00:06:25.504 --> 00:06:28.890
ober azoy vi undz ze'mir, m'hot undz avekgenumen

00:06:29.757 --> 00:06:31.928
hot men undz ales avekgenumen.

00:06:32.136 --> 00:06:34.588
m'hot bald aroysgetrogn dos mebl.

00:06:34.588 --> 00:06:38.115
kh'hob derkent bay eyne, bay eyne a goyishe

00:06:38.115 --> 00:06:40.635
hob ikh derkent undzere a shafe

00:06:41.485 --> 00:06:43.807
un zi hot zi nisht gevolt mir opgebn

00:06:44.809 --> 00:06:48.872
un di kikh iz bayn undz gevezn zeyer sheyn aryngerikhtet, a

00:06:48.872 --> 00:06:52.227
tshekhisher tishler hot undz gemakht a

00:06:53.517 --> 00:06:54.366
a

00:06:54.366 --> 00:06:55.468
in kokh

00:06:55.609 --> 00:06:56.767
aza

00:06:57.837 --> 00:07:00.278
kokh kredenze hot dos geheysn

00:07:00.570 --> 00:07:07.215
vos dos hot men nisht, m'hot dos gekent ⟨zi tsenemen⟩ un aroystrogn, nor keyner hot nisht gevust vi azoy dos tsu nemen.

00:07:07.215 --> 00:07:09.814
dos hot er gemakht nokh a zhurnal

00:07:09.814 --> 00:07:12.641
fun Prag hot er bashtelt di gantse

00:07:12.641 --> 00:07:14.362
tsugehern dertsu

00:07:14.362 --> 00:07:15.695
dos tsu makhn

00:07:15.695 --> 00:07:19.751
zenen gekumen dernokh dem di andere aropnemen dos muster fun dem

00:07:19.825 --> 00:07:24.206
dos iz geblibn in kokh, far deys hobn zey nisht gekent aroystrogn.

00:07:25.630 --> 00:07:29.542
un dan iz gevezn in kokh, hot er oykhet gemakht zeyer a sheyn

00:07:29.542 --> 00:07:33.254
UNK televizye iz nokh nisht geven demolts, a radyo tishl.

00:07:33.254 --> 00:07:36.207
dos iz gevezn herlekh gemakht epes.

00:07:36.207 --> 00:07:37.858
dos iz gevezn

00:07:38.843 --> 00:07:41.168
hintn mit tsvey tirlekh

00:07:41.168 --> 00:07:46.180
a bisl hekher geven nor eyn tirl oyftsumakhn. dortn iz geven nor broyt tsu haltn.

00:07:46.180 --> 00:07:48.669
in der zayt iz gevezn ledelekh.

00:07:48.669 --> 00:07:50.517
dort hot di mame gehaltn

00:07:50.517 --> 00:07:51.611
ire

00:07:51.668 --> 00:07:52.691
mh

00:07:52.714 --> 00:07:54.778
ire zakhn

00:07:54.778 --> 00:07:57.905
 kremen mit puder mit vos.

00:07:57.979 --> 00:08:02.819
oyf dem iz gevezn gemakht aza sheyn UNK shpigele. dos iz geven

00:08:02.819 --> 00:08:05.586
keyn mol vel ikh dos nisht fargesn vi sheyn dos iz geven.

00:08:05.586 --> 00:08:10.376
dos hot oykhet a goy tsugenumen, un an anderer goy hot undz gezogt dos iz bayn im.

00:08:10.635 --> 00:08:13.042
un ikh bin gegangen dos opbetn

00:08:13.217 --> 00:08:15.354
hot er es nisht gevolt opgebn.

00:08:15.951 --> 00:08:18.425
zi, di froy hot nisht gevolt opgebn.

00:08:18.870 --> 00:08:22.104
un er hot gezogt yo gebn, un zi hot nisht gevolt opgebn.

00:08:22.161 --> 00:08:26.779
zog ikh der froy, "kuk, az d'vest dikh azoy aynshparn, gey ikh un ikh breng aher

00:08:26.852 --> 00:08:28.283
dem politsey

00:08:28.283 --> 00:08:33.140
un d'vest dos yo opgebn, far ikh hob es shoyn gezen az s'iz do bay dir. du kenst shoyn nisht opleykenen."

00:08:33.687 --> 00:08:36.482
azoy vos deys hobn zey hobn yo opgegebn

00:08:37.179 --> 00:08:43.585
ober vayter hobn mir nisht gehat gornisht. s'iz nisht gevezn keyn telers, s'iz nisht geven keyn lefl, s'iz nisht geven keyn

00:08:43.592 --> 00:08:46.078
tepl un vos epes optsukokhn

00:08:46.078 --> 00:08:49.217
gornisht, absolut gornisht hob ikh nisht gehat.

00:08:49.217 --> 00:08:50.790
dos ales hob ikh gedarft

00:08:50.790 --> 00:08:55.398
koyfn far gelt mayne zakhn, dernokh fun di goyim opkoyfn az ikh zol epes hobn.

00:08:55.928 --> 00:08:58.706
ABER DIE LEUT- ANASHIM YATSU MIN HABAYIT.

00:08:58.628 --> 00:08:59.398
yo.

00:08:59.674 --> 00:09:00.478
yo.

00:09:01.800 --> 00:09:03.701
yo, zenen aroys

00:09:03.707 --> 00:09:09.213
un vos iz nokh geblibn dortn, hobn mir gehat a verande, zeyer a groyse a lange, un dort iz gevezn

00:09:09.213 --> 00:09:13.171
a SHATIACH aza langer, hot undz a tsveyte shkheyne dertseylt

00:09:13.171 --> 00:09:16.352
az zey hobn shoyn gehert az undz ze'mir aheymgekumen

00:09:16.352 --> 00:09:19.901
hobn zey shoyn dem SHATIACH oyfgehoybn un a- avekgetrogn.

00:09:22.472 --> 00:09:23.242
ha

00:09:24.058 --> 00:09:26.566
vos zol ikh aykh dertseyln? dos iz shoyn

00:09:27.990 --> 00:09:30.852
dos iz oykhet geven shver, trefn a lere shtub.

00:09:32.715 --> 00:09:36.134
KAMA ZMAN CHIKIT AD SHEACH SHELACH HIGIA?

00:09:37.086 --> 00:09:40.016
EH, LO ZOCHERET BIDIUK, EH

00:09:40.309 --> 00:09:41.653
KAMA SHAVUOT.

00:09:44.690 --> 00:09:46.850
AT YECHOLA LEDABER BEYIDISH EH

00:09:44.713 --> 00:09:46.782
oy, far vos?

00:09:48.257 --> 00:09:50.445
VEHU CHAZAR HABAITA

00:09:50.265 --> 00:09:52.469
er iz aheymgekumen

00:09:52.198 --> 00:09:53.858
VEMAHU YADA?

00:09:52.577 --> 00:09:56.098
un er hot zikh arumgekukt. er iz gevezn a yung kind.

00:09:56.155 --> 00:09:59.018
er hot zikh arumgekukt aher, ahin

00:09:59.513 --> 00:10:02.966
biz er hot gezen dos iz nisht far im

00:10:03.310 --> 00:10:06.268
un er hot gedarft gevezn bald geyn

00:10:06.268 --> 00:10:07.910
in di rusishe

00:10:08.406 --> 00:10:10.189
ARMIYA dinen

00:10:10.903 --> 00:10:13.141
nokh a shtikl tsayt, nokh a yor

00:10:14.295 --> 00:10:15.622
afile f-

00:10:15.696 --> 00:10:18.035
a yor hot er, a bisl nokh mer

00:10:18.042 --> 00:10:20.010
un er mit khaveyrim

00:10:21.568 --> 00:10:24.262
hobn zikh tsunoyfgeshmuest, zoln antloyfn

00:10:25.298 --> 00:10:28.515
un dos iz gevezn azoy shver tsu antloyfn.

00:10:28.521 --> 00:10:31.241
vi azoy ikh hob shoyn gezogt, di rusishe grenets

00:10:31.241 --> 00:10:35.711
iber di rusishe grenets hot afile a feygele nisht getort durkhflien.

00:10:37.060 --> 00:10:39.923
un az zey hobn zikh tsunoyfgeshmuest

00:10:40.941 --> 00:10:44.259
un ikh hob gevust, mer keyner

00:10:44.468 --> 00:10:49.356
un dem tog vos er hot gedarft antloyfn, dos iz geven z- in a zuntik tog

00:10:50.104 --> 00:10:51.380
mayn

00:10:52.787 --> 00:10:54.994
shviger foter iz gevezn

00:10:54.994 --> 00:10:56.122
krank,

00:10:56.263 --> 00:10:59.142
zeyer krank, un ikh bin mit im geforn

00:10:59.318 --> 00:11:01.337
in an andere shtot

00:11:01.798 --> 00:11:05.302
tsun a dokter. di shtot hot geheysn Beregsaz

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:08.862
un ikh hob ibergelebt in dem tog

00:11:09.966 --> 00:11:13.807
hob ikh moyre gezogt az me zol im nisht khapn, dem bruder.

00:11:13.915 --> 00:11:16.760
dos iz geven shreklekh vos ikh hob ibergelebt.

00:11:17.323 --> 00:11:19.915
undz ze'mir aheymgekumen oyf der nakht

00:11:20.023 --> 00:11:21.395
un ikh ze

00:11:21.395 --> 00:11:25.876
do shteyt a por mentshn redn. dort shteyt a por mentshn, yidishe

00:11:25.876 --> 00:11:26.947
un redn

00:11:26.947 --> 00:11:29.889
un ikh hob moyre gehat tsi m'hot im nisht

00:11:29.963 --> 00:11:30.969
gekhapt.

00:11:31.752 --> 00:11:34.226
eyner kumt tsu tsu mir, zogt er

00:11:34.367 --> 00:11:35.896
"vu iz dayn bruder?"

00:11:36.190 --> 00:11:41.162
zog ikh "ikh veys nisht. ikh bin nisht geven in der heym. ikh bin geven in Beregsaz."

00:11:45.387 --> 00:11:48.519
zogt er "du veyst, dayn bruder iz antlofn."

00:11:49.453 --> 00:11:52.872
zog ikh "vos du zogst nisht," makh ikh im azoy

00:11:54.010 --> 00:11:56.788
un ikh bin shoyn gevezn gliklekh vi di velt

00:11:56.963 --> 00:12:00.585
az er iz antlofn, az oyf der nakht az m'hot im nisht gekhapt.

00:12:01.435 --> 00:12:04.905
un er hot zikh nebekh ongeplogt genug far dem antloyfn

00:12:05.299 --> 00:12:07.621
biz er iz ongekumen aher

00:12:08.303 --> 00:12:11.185
az er hot zikh ongeplogt. er iz ongekumen

00:12:11.185 --> 00:12:15.030
durkh, geshvumen a, a vaser a groys.

00:12:15.745 --> 00:12:17.814
s'hot geheysn di TISZA

00:12:18.057 --> 00:12:20.565
biz er UNK iz gekumen in Rumenye

00:12:20.706 --> 00:12:23.942
un in Rumenye biz vi lang hot er zikh gedarft bahaltn

00:12:23.942 --> 00:12:26.364
⟨biz lang⟩ er zol kenen vayter forn

00:12:26.364 --> 00:12:28.457
azoy iz er vayter geforn

00:12:28.457 --> 00:12:29.427
biz

00:12:33.092 --> 00:12:34.588
NAGYVARAD

00:12:34.932 --> 00:12:37.592
un fun dortn iz er geforn

00:12:37.918 --> 00:12:39.498
keyn BUDAPEST

00:12:41.783 --> 00:12:44.291
un fun BUDAPEST iz er geforn

00:12:45.090 --> 00:12:46.530
keyn Italye.

00:12:46.530 --> 00:12:49.168
er hot zikh dort opgevalgert a shtik tsayt.

00:12:49.596 --> 00:12:51.761
far m'hot nisht gekent kumen aher.

00:12:51.761 --> 00:12:56.323
m'hot, m'hot gekhapt di shifn mit di yunge kinder. m'hot nisht arayngelozt.

00:12:56.970 --> 00:13:00.187
dernokh ⟨farshtey iz⟩ er gekumen durkh Kafrisn

00:13:00.531 --> 00:13:03.967
un iz ongekumen do in akht un fertsiker yor

00:13:05.847 --> 00:13:07.090
in HAIFA.

00:13:07.197 --> 00:13:09.682
oyf di shif hot men im shoyn gegebn

00:13:09.682 --> 00:13:12.036
a, a holtsern biksl

00:13:12.036 --> 00:13:14.044
un er zol geyn in der milkhome.

00:13:14.044 --> 00:13:16.252
un er ken nisht redn, un er

00:13:16.490 --> 00:13:17.150
nu

00:13:17.150 --> 00:13:18.092
vi azoy

00:13:19.127 --> 00:13:20.103
azoy

00:13:20.103 --> 00:13:23.188
hot er nebekh do mitgemakht ale milkhomes

00:13:23.278 --> 00:13:24.892
ale milkhomes

00:13:25.185 --> 00:13:30.067
di shverste milkhomes zenen geven deys vos er hot farloyrn zayn tokhter

00:13:30.067 --> 00:13:32.368
zayn fertsik yerike tokhter

00:13:33.758 --> 00:13:35.912
a sheyne, a kluge

00:13:39.107 --> 00:13:41.716
hot ibergelozt dray kinder

00:13:45.469 --> 00:13:48.888
deys iz UNK gevezn di shverste milkhome fun ale.

00:14:48.649 --> 00:14:51.039
FRIDA, BEEZE SHANA HITCHATANT?

00:14:52.108 --> 00:14:53.081
zib-

