UNK

00:27:09.698 --> 00:27:12.180
FRIDA, MI ZE PO BATMUNA?

00:27:13.022 --> 00:27:15.716
dos iz mayne shviger eltern

00:27:15.840 --> 00:27:17.302
mit di kinder.

00:27:17.359 --> 00:27:19.327
dos kleyntshike kind

00:27:19.350 --> 00:27:21.133
dos iz gevezn mayn man.

00:27:22.135 --> 00:27:24.910
VEMI NISHAR BEMISHPACHA ZOT HI?

00:27:24.910 --> 00:27:26.042
Kleyner.

00:27:26.742 --> 00:27:28.170
HAABA UNK

00:27:27.130 --> 00:27:29.267
der groys- Kleyner

00:27:29.762 --> 00:27:34.379
der ABA iz geblibn lebn, ober er iz geshtorbn dernokh dem, dem

00:27:34.943 --> 00:27:37.046
akh un fertsikstn yor.

00:27:37.920 --> 00:27:40.505
AT YODAAT ET HASHEMOT SHELAHEM?

00:27:40.528 --> 00:27:41.349
yo.

00:27:42.148 --> 00:27:43.390
TISAPER LANU.

00:27:42.368 --> 00:27:43.350
yo

00:27:43.532 --> 00:27:46.100
BETSAD YAMIN, HAYELED

00:27:45.996 --> 00:27:48.065
dos iz MENDI

00:27:48.122 --> 00:27:50.532
velekher er iz gefaln do

00:27:50.532 --> 00:27:53.954
in der milkhome in akht un fertsikstn yor.

00:27:54.332 --> 00:27:56.621
er iz baerdikt in

00:27:58.483 --> 00:27:59.880
vi azoy heyst?

00:27:59.880 --> 00:28:01.649
in KFAR VARBURG.

00:28:02.061 --> 00:28:03.651
un dos meydele?

00:28:03.160 --> 00:28:05.821
dos meydele iz gevezn RUCHI

00:28:05.821 --> 00:28:07.168
hot zi geheysn.

00:28:07.174 --> 00:28:11.589
zi iz gevezn shoyn groys, avek mit der mame in krematorium.

00:28:13.013 --> 00:28:15.003
VEHASHEM SHEL HAIMA?

00:28:15.477 --> 00:28:16.804
Khaye Reyzl

00:28:18.143 --> 00:28:20.426
azoy vi mayn eynikl heyst.

00:28:20.426 --> 00:28:21.428
YARIT.

00:28:24.657 --> 00:28:27.098
ET HAKREMATORIUM. LO ROTS-

00:28:26.361 --> 00:28:28.869
K- KEN. YESH, ROTSE, NACHON UNK

00:28:30.799 --> 00:28:35.146
FRIDA, MA ANACHNU ROIM BATMUNA ZOT HI MEAVODA SHEL UNK?

00:28:37.414 --> 00:28:45.795
leyder, do zet men vi s'iz gevezn oysgegrobn groyse griber, un m'hot gemakht a fayer un geforn di mentshn in fayer arayn.

00:28:45.868 --> 00:28:49.490
lebedike mentshn hot men arayngevorfn dort in fayer.

00:28:49.834 --> 00:28:52.580
UNK EFO YESH LACH ET HATMUNA HAZOT?

00:28:52.669 --> 00:28:55.683
dey TMUNA hot mayn got zeliker man

00:28:55.892 --> 00:28:57.320
gekoyft

00:28:58.407 --> 00:29:01.890
ikh veys nisht fun vemen. ikh gedenk nisht fun vemen.
